N2  - This article focuses on developing an agenda for business ethics research. Thirty-two researchers were enlisted to review the conduct of the field, and four underlying images that guide their work are outlined. Research questions are articulated to translate those images into concrete behaviors for both practitioners and researchers in the ethics field.
